  "description": "Welcome! St. John is a place where a very diverse and active congregation enjoys the rich traditions of the Episcopal church. The church building is located on the Oregon Episcopal School campus in southwest Portland, Oregon, at 6300 SW Nicol Road. You can find us at the top of the hill, next to the bell",
  "htmlMain": "<p><a href=\"http://wheretraditionwelcomesdiversity.org\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-993\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-300x52.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-300x52.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-768x132.jpg 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-1024x176.jpg 1024w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-100x17.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-150x26.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-200x34.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-450x77.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-600x103.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo-900x155.jpg 900w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/St-John-the-Baptist-parish-logo.jpg 1121w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 473px) 100vw, 473px\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #666666;\">Welcome! St. John is <wbr>a <wbr>place <wbr>where a very diverse and active congregation enjoys the <wbr>rich traditions of the Episcopal church. The church building is located on the Oregon Episcopal School campus in southwest Portland, Oregon, at 6300 SW Nicol Road. You can find us at the top of the hill, next to the bell tower.</span></p>\n<div id=\"io-ox-core\" class=\"abs unselectable\">\n<div id=\"io-ox-screens\" class=\"abs\">\n<div id=\"io-ox-windowmanager\" class=\"abs\">\n<div id=\"io-ox-windowmanager-pane\" class=\"atb\">\n<div id=\"window-0\" class=\"window-container io-ox-mail-window chromeless-window\" data-window-nr=\"0\" data-app-name=\"io.ox/mail\">\n<div class=\"window-container-center\">\n<div class=\"window-body classic-toolbar-visible\">\n<div class=\"abs window-content vsplit preview-right\">\n<div class=\"rightside mail-detail-pane selection-one\" data-page-id=\"undefined/detailView\">\n<div class=\"thread-view-control abs\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"thread-view-list scrollable abs\">\n<div class=\"thread-view list-view\">\n<article class=\"list-item mail-item mail-detail f6-target expanded\" tabindex=\"1\" data-loaded=\"true\" data-cid=\"default0/INBOX.1494449579072241964\">\n<section class=\"body user-select-text\" tabindex=\"1\">\n<div class=\"mail-detail-content noI18n colorQuoted simple-mail\">\n<div id=\"ox-4b99b523dd\">\n<div class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-WordSection1\">\n<p class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #444444;\">Our Mission</span></p>\n<p class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #666666;\">As the Episcopal Parish of St. John the Baptist, we strive to share the Good News of God, to grow as Christian disciples, and to respond to the needs of the world in the power of the Holy Spirit.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #666666;\">We do this by putting our faith into action through worship, education, reflection, and ministry to others. You can learn more about ministries and church activities by reading our Faith In Action blog, watching sermons on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCO4lYcpVDiHOF5rywyVedow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">YouTube</a>, or visiting our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wheretraditionwelcomesdiversity\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Facebook Page</a>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.0pt; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #444444;\">Our Community</span></p>\n<p class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #666666;\">We are an inclusive community where all are welcomed to come and explore their relationship with God. All baptized Christians (not just our members) are invited to join us in Holy Communion. While you are here, you will also be able relax in a peaceful environment, find joy in the music, listen to engaging sermons, and enjoy good fellowship with the others who have found their church home.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; color: #666666;\">Please call the Parish Office at (503) 245-3777 or sign the guest register so we can connect you with our Welcome Team.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ox-4b99b523dd-MsoNormal\"><a href=\"http://wheretraditionwelcomesdiversity.org/\">http://wheretraditionwelcomesdiversity.org/</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</article>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t"
}